44
00:02:31,833 --> 00:02:33,354
As you walked slowly toward me

45
00:02:33,354 --> 00:02:34,753
and put that bracelet on my wrist,

46
00:02:36,873 --> 00:02:38,074
I felt really happy.

47
00:02:43,354 --> 00:02:44,234
I know

48
00:02:44,593 --> 00:02:46,273
