52
00:02:52,234 --> 00:02:54,313
But I've explained myself.

53
00:02:54,313 --> 00:02:55,033
I know.

54
00:02:58,273 --> 00:02:59,993
So, I began to understand you

55
00:03:01,433 --> 00:03:02,914
