56
00:03:02,914 --> 00:03:04,474
I accept your apology.

57
00:03:06,553 --> 00:03:07,674
But why?

58
00:03:09,194 --> 00:03:10,354
Because I'm afraid.

59
00:03:11,234 --> 00:03:13,313
