will continue to haunt us.

63
00:03:18,914 --> 00:03:19,433
But there's no love

64
00:03:19,433 --> 00:03:21,394
between us.

65
00:03:21,394 --> 00:03:22,394
I know.

66
00:03:23,194 --> 00:03:25,033
Can you assure me

67
00:03:25,394 --> 00:03:26,514
this is the last time

68
00:03:26,514 --> 00:03:28,394
